<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Killed the base64 bloat</span> - That <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">id="brian-photo"</code> was 400+ lines of garbage. Now it's just <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">&lt;img src="assets/brian.jpg" alt="Brian K. - Full-Stack Developer"&gt;</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Your <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">&lt;body&gt;</code> is HUGE</span> - 421,012 characters. That's why your file felt slow. Tailwind utilities everywhere.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Next move</span>: I'm converting the whole thing to pure HTML/CSS. No Tailwind CDN, no build step.</li>
</ol>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Here's the updated start of your file</span></h3>
<p>Replace your <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">&lt;head&gt;</code> + that base64 <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">&lt;img&gt;</code> with this. The rest of your body will work, but we'll clean it next:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="markdown-content min-w-0"><div class="stack mx-auto flex max-w-3xl min-w-0 flex-col items-center overflow-visible"><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div><div><div class="bg-bg-secondary border-fill-divider rounded-8 overflow-hidden border"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="relative w-full cursor-pointer overflow-hidden bg-white [&amp;&gt;*]:pointer-events-none" aria-label="Open preview" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;"><iframe sandbox="allow-scripts allow-forms allow-same-origin" class="h-full w-full border-0 bg-white transition-opacity duration-200" scrolling="no" title="HTML preview" src="./Brian_files/a4a627b9-1410-47dd-8226-856264dec738.html" style="background-color: rgb(23, 23, 26); opacity: 1; width: 151.884%; height: 151.884%; transform: scale(0.658398); transform-origin: left top;"></iframe></div><div class="bg-fill-primary text-text-secondary flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-3 justify-end"><span data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><div class="contents"><button aria-label="Share" class="enabled:active:scale-98 inline-flex shrink-0 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-round focus:not-focus-visible:outline-none transition-transform duration-150 ease-in-out disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 select-none size-7 hover:enabled:bg-fill-secondary-elevated enabled:active:filter-[brightness(0.965)] dark:enabled:active:filter-[brightness(0.9)]" data-slot="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" width="20" height="20" class="m-0.5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24.692 4.965c.331-.091.768-.179 1.202-.031.551.187.985