span></span><span class="block before:content-[counter(line)] before:inline-block before:[counter-increment:line] before:w-6 before:mr-4 before:text-[13px] before:text-right before:text-muted-foreground/50 before:font-mono before:select-none"><span class="text-[var(--sdm-c,inherit)] dark:text-[var(--shiki-dark,var(--sdm-c,inherit))]">brian.jpg         →  brian.jpg    ← Keep same</span></span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="markdown-content min-w-0"><div class="stack mx-auto flex max-w-3xl min-w-0 flex-col items-center overflow-visible"><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div><div dir="auto" class="ur-markdown prose prose-trimmed citation-aware"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">2. Upload to GitHub - 2 ways</span></h3>
<h4 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-lg" data-streamdown="heading-4"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Option A: Drag &amp; Drop - Easiest</span></h4>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Go to github.com → Click <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">+</code> → <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">New repository</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Repo name: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">brian-portfolio</code> or <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">zuri-creative-designs</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Check <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">Public</code> → <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">Create repository</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Click <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">uploading an existing file</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Drag <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">index.html</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">style.css</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">brian.jpg</code> into the box</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Commit message: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">Initial portfolio upload</code> → <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">Commit changes</code></li>
</ol>
