unded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">main.css</code></p></div></div></td><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>Keep it simple. Avoid <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">style-v2-final.css</code></p></div></div></td></tr><tr class="border-color-(--fill-divider) border-t border-solid"><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline [&amp;_*]:font-medium"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>Images</p></div></div></td><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">brian.jpg</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">hero.jpg</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">project-1.png</code></p></div></div></td><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>Lowercase, no spaces. Use <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">-</code> not <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">_</code> for SEO</p></div></div></td></tr><tr class="border-color-(--fill-divider) border-t border-solid"><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline [&amp;_*]:font-medium"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>Folders</p></div></div></td><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">assets/</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">images/</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">css/</code></p></div></div></td><td class="text-subheadline leading-[22px] text-text-primary py-2 px-4 text-start align-top break-words first:ps-0"><div dir="auto" class="prose [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:gap-0 [&amp;_*]:text-subheadline"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>If you get more files later</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="flex justify-end"><div class="contents"><