ass="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Repo name ideas:</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">brian-portfolio</code> - Clean, professional</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">zuri-creative-designs</code> - Brand name</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">brian-k-dev</code> - Personal brand</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Avoid: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">website</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">test</code>, <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">index_90</code> - not descriptive</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">5. What to do right after upload</span></h3>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Check your image path</span>: In <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">index.html</code> make sure it says <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">src="brian.jpg"</code> not <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">src="/mnt/data/brian.jpg"</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Add a README.md</span>: GitHub shows this on your repo page. 1 line is fine:</li>
