"3zGHt8\":\"Manus web browser\",\"2QPTUW\":\"Media not found\",\"4uiHzi\":\"Close\",\"1YXLFy\":\"Create, remix and share AI videos\",\"4tWcui\":\"Describe your animation...\",\"4hJlxC\":\"Animate my photo\",\"1xg8bF\":\"Create an image of a 90s robot\",\"3puy9D\":\"Restyle my photo as 3D\",\"XNu2o\":\"Create and edit images in seconds\",\"1yOD1b\":\"Instantly generate high-quality images with simple text prompts, or upload your own to transform them into something completely new. Change or remove backgrounds, switch outfits and more to create fun memes to share with friends, tell new stories or express yourself through striking art creations.\",\"2iGSWH\":\"Create an AI image\",\"mwmeE\":\"AI video generation example\",\"JhtHf\":\"Bring your creations to life\",\"1eMkGC\":\"Create vibes – expressive AI-generated videos – by animating your images with the click of a button or describing exactly what you want with custom animation prompts. You can also extend your videos, restyle them and add music.\",\"FHZv1\":\"Create an AI video\",\"1aXPMi\":\"AI video animation example\",\"2mUnoG\":\"Get inspired and try new ideas\",\"GDMjC\":\"Dive into an immersive feed of creative, expressive AI-generated videos from the community. Remix your favourite vibes to instantly try new ideas and put your own unique spin on them.\",\"4iSjSr\":\"Get started\",\"2VDjhP\":\"Community AI video examples\",\"1V5OAw\":\"Share and connect in new ways\",\"4hxhZq\":\"Share your vibes with friends and spark new conversations, or publish them to the Meta AI feed to inspire a community of AI creators.\",\"18sHic\":\"Share your art\",\"4dzWGF\":\"Sharing AI videos example\",\"2H1Ir3\":\"Explore Meta AI's image and video editing and generation capabilities\",\"3k5oFp\":\"Custom animations icon\",\"2aSDkL\":\"Create custom animations\",\"Mp6Ny\":\"Bring your exact vision to life with text prompts for custom animations.\",\"2jjJDC\":\"Edit images icon\",\"2DUyob\":\"Edit images\",\"3kJ8Uj\":\"Upload an image and transform objects, backgrounds and more.\",\"4omYfj\":\"Extend videos icon\",\"G47h9\":\"Extend videos\",\"2PLr43\":\"Make your videos longer with just one click.\",\"4xqbOe\":\"Get more done icon\",\"4y3CkV\":\"Get more done\",\"3EDC6W\":\"Tap into advanced tools to adjust variety, uniqueness and more.\",\"20TjjF\":\"View creations icon\",\"2UbNW7\":\"View your creations\",\"461omF\":\"See all of your media in one place and in the creation gallery.\",\"uj0jn\":\"Restyle and edit icon\",\"2GCgGB\":\"Restyle and edit\",\"3WA1rk\":\"Instantly restyle your videos with presets or make precise edits.\",\"yYZxj\":\"Meta AI\",\"3tStIE\":\"AI image generator\",\"2o0aIP\":\"AI image and video generator\",\"3ERRUu\":\"Create AI images and videos\",\"4e5LiV\":\"Create an image...\",\"3kZe6K\":\"Animate my photo\",\"3vSg5S\":\"Create an image of a 90s robot\",\"qx4m2\":\"Restyle my photo as 3D\",\"3YZIRC\":\"Create an image of a dog as a king\",\"saAux\":\"Create AI images in seconds\",\"unKxM\":\"Bring your idea to life by using Meta AI to create stunning AI images. Start with a simple text prompt to generate any AI image. Unlock your imagination by using Meta AI's image generator and start creating AI images – whether it is a meme for fun, an infographic for a school project, or an AI image of yourself.\",\"BOSNL\":\"Create an AI image\",\"1sOwmi\":\"AI-generated image examples\",\"X4Cf\":\"Animate any image with AI\",\"3qDhFh\":\"Unleash your creativity with Meta AI's animation capabilities. Create any AI image, then ask Meta AI to animate it. You can also upload your own images and animate them. Share your AI animations with the community and get inspired by new ideas. With Meta AI, the art of animating images knows no bounds.\",\"zFDlz\":\"Animate an image with AI\",\"43Oplb\":\"AI animation example\",\"3yOzHR\":\"Edit your own images with AI\",\"2Pd1gE\":\"Turn yourself into an expert designer by using Meta AI's image editing features. Upload any image, then ask Meta AI to add or change parts of the image. You can also use Meta AI as a background remover or restyle the image using dozens of AI styles, colours and lighting options – from anime and painting to moody and sunset lighting.\",\"3BPE26\":\"Edit an image with AI\",\"r3RYI\":\"AI image editing examples\",\"1aRwJP\":\"Explore Meta AI's image and video editing and generation capabilities\",\"1jorZh\":\"Create images icon\",\"4avj1s\":\"Create images\",\"39fujj\":\"Bring any idea to life with a simple text prompt.\",\"3xYrlx\":\"Create an image of yourself icon\",\"3khKEB\":\"Create an image of yourself\",\"2xiiM3\":\"Picture yourself on the moon, try a new hairstyle and more.\",\"3Csrag\":\"Edit images icon\",\"ZC6nL\":\"Edit images\",\"2joW4q\":\"Add, remove or change parts of your image.\",\"25qEXy\":\"Restyle images icon\",\"2fR5rp\":\"Restyle images\",\"4kXlLy\":\"Explore our library of styles to restyle your images in one click.\",\"2wTBZs\":\"Animate images icon\",\"3sWKip\":\"Animate images\",\"fm0h3\":\"Turn images you create or upload into animations.\",\"2bn6Iz\":\"Analyse images icon\",\"21sgXl\":\"Analyse images\",\"2397NU\":\"Ask any question about an image.\",\"19QHem\":\"Dismiss\",\"BRfT3\":\"Cancel upload\",\"oXXAw\":\"Uploading file...\",\"1QVq4D\":\"This may take a moment\",\"20tydv\":\"Upload file\",\"3fMQ6J\":\"Upload a file or paste a URL\",\"3AtRNT\":\"Submit URL\",\"CIBXS\":\"Supports JPEG, PNG, WEBP, GIF, MP4 and MOV files. Direct links must be publicly accessible.\",\"389u3l\":\"Meta\",\"29l18a\":\"Meta AI\",\"1DAyxT\":\"Information about content credentials and how we know this information. {=m2}\",\"4qPdv9\":\"Learn more\",\"3KShzb\":\"Dismiss result\",\"39GPQn\":\"No Meta AI signatures were found\",\"3LCtfr\":\"We were not able to find information about generative AI use by Meta AI in this file.\",\"4yMvk3\":\"Identify files created or edited with AI\",\"n4Hrd\":\"Upload a file to find out more about whether it's been created or edited by