0794156\",\"text\":\"Restyle my photo as a stamp\",\"longPrompt\":\"Transform the subject into a commemorative postage stamp design, illustrated in fine engraved linework. Apply rich, stylised colours such as cobalt blues, crimson reds or emerald greens, while keeping the engraved texture and linework visible. Frame the subject within a rectangular stamp border with perforated edges and visible paper texture so that it reads as a physical printed object. Place a single number \\\"8\\\" in one corner as the denomination. Do not include any other text, words or letters. Present the stamp alone, isolated on a neutral background, making it look like a photograph of an authentic collectible postage stamp featuring the subject.\",\"type\":\"imagine_media_picker\",\"attachment_type\":\"MEDIA_PICKER\",\"category\":null,\"responseDisplayMode\":null},{\"id\":\"1057199902931162\",\"text\":\"Create an image of a watercolour painting of a cat\",\"longPrompt\":\"Create an image of a watercolour painting of a cat\",\"type\":\"imagine\",\"attachment_type\":\"NONE\",\"category\":null,\"responseDisplayMode\":null},{\"id\":\"2673567376316532\",\"text\":\"Create an image of a hiker on an avocado\",\"longPrompt\":\"Create an image of a woman. She is clad in minimalist miniature hiking gear, standing with quiet triumph on a vibrant avocado. The avocado's surface is subtly dew-kissed, diffused daylight with gentle, clean highlights. The composition is clean and uncluttered, emphasising the dreamlike scale.\",\"type\":\"imagine\",\"attachment_type\":\"NONE\",\"category\":null,\"responseDisplayMode\":null},{\"id\":\"25050773674508010\",\"text\":\"Create an image of a 90s robot\",\"longPrompt\":\"Create an image of a detailed, hand-painted plastic model of a 90s-era giant Japanese transforming robot set in a diorama. The robot is posed in an action stance, capturing dynamic movement. The scene is viewed from an upward-angle shot taken with a mobile phone, giving it a dramatic yet homemade, gritty quality that enhances the nostalgic, action-packed feel of the scene.\",\"type\":\"imagine\",\"attachment_type\":\"NONE\",\"category\":null,\"responseDisplayMode\":null}]}}\n"])</script><script nonce="">$RC("B:26","S:26")</script><script nonce="">self.__next_f.push([1,"70:{\"data\":{\"viewer\":{\"__typename\":\"Ecto1ViewerContext\",\"__isIViewerContext\":\"Ecto1ViewerContext\",\"fetaEntrypointTitle\":null,\"fetaEntrypointSubtitle\":null,\"isEligibleToSeeMetaSubsEP\":false,\"tosRegion\":\"ROW\",\"socialProfile\":{\"username\":\"yobrai\",\"profile_picture\":\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/yd/r/_tN6hYY4oeH.webp\"},\"id\":\"viewer:2c8e5ee5-4f48-47dd-ad4e-43a11c6aeb0a\"}}}\n"])</script><link rel="preload" as="image" href="./Brian_files/_tN6hYY4oeH.webp"><script nonce="">$RC("B:1a","S:1a")</script><script nonce="">$RC("B:1c","S:1c")</script><script nonce="">self.__next_f.push([1,"6f:{\"data\":{\"pinnedConversations\":{\"edges\":[],\"pageInfo\":{\"endCursor\":null,\"hasNextPage\":false}},\"unpinnedConversations\":{\"edges\":[{\"node\":{\"id\":\"b7b53b3e-ca29-4971-a47c-9021b3547396\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-29T10:57:33.000Z\",\"conversationId\":\"1098740049996220\",\"title\":\"this is my html file, help me correct it and break it down, make it pure human code,break them down to files so i can create a repository in Github\",\"displayTitle\":\"this is my html file, help me correct it and break it down, make it pure human code,break them down to files so i can create a repository in Github\",\"pinned\":false,\"matchingSnippet\":null,\"matchingSnippets\":null,\"type\":\"CHAT\",\"__typename\":\"Conversation\"},\"cursor\":\"QVFIU2lUYkU1NGUybUktQXhRYzRoLU5MYnV1WEQ0bmlOV0diWmRpbldVRnRCWmtsRzFSUHdUWXQ3THlua3U3UUVFcENmNUlwbHNiNTFLalBEcGRQcEVlZATl3\"},{\"node\":{\"id\":\"8dd65892-aecf-4371-8055-b3e403bd7c48\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-24T16:16:59.000Z\",\"conversationId\":\"1091619020708323\",\"title\":\"Adding my WhatsApp number\",\"displayTitle\":\"Adding my WhatsApp num